    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to your happy place.<br><br>'ROOST' is a brief first-person horror game, set in the English town of Mournbrough - a place harbouring dark secrets and seemingly lost to time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Player assumes the role of Declan Harker; a down-on-his-luck paranormal investigator who has been drawn to a haunting mystery where their quest for answers quickly spirals into a personal nightmare. <br> <br>A haunting mystery. A personal nightmare. Overcome your fears. Uncover the truth.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heavily inspired by <u><i>P.T.</i></u>, <u><i>Paratopic</i>, </u> <u><i>Silent Hill</i></u> , <u><i>Se7en</i></u>, <u><i>Lost Highway</i></u> and the work of <u>Kyoshi Kurosawa</u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >| 'CRUEL BRITANNIA' |</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/35419f1c53f2dc05c945fb6534007dc0.poster.avif?t=1758639690\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/35419f1c53f2dc05c945fb6534007dc0.webm?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/35419f1c53f2dc05c945fb6534007dc0.mp4?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The games visual direction borrows heavily from PSX era, but channeled through a bleak vision of the forgotten realm of northern England.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >| IT'S GRIM UP NORTH |</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A regional tale, set in the North-East of England. Inspired by the stories, perceptions and tales of the area. Welcome to Mournbrough. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/4060603d32dad7695fe31c1de73bc9cf.poster.avif?t=1758639690\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/4060603d32dad7695fe31c1de73bc9cf.webm?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/4060603d32dad7695fe31c1de73bc9cf.mp4?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >| ATMOSPHERIC WORLD AND SOUND DESIGN |</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The town has many sights to see, and plenty of things you don't want to hear. Every nook and cranny has a story to tell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/2339a4610a5240c4ca3e03ada38502c9.poster.avif?t=1758639690\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/2339a4610a5240c4ca3e03ada38502c9.webm?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/2339a4610a5240c4ca3e03ada38502c9.mp4?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >| MAKE CONVERSATION |</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >People make the world go round. Get to know them or keep your distance. Never judge a book by it's cover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/5f3815e5ecfd76ba030ad05add183ce0.poster.avif?t=1758639690\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/5f3815e5ecfd76ba030ad05add183ce0.webm?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/5f3815e5ecfd76ba030ad05add183ce0.mp4?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >| A JOURNEY LIKE NO OTHER |</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Getting to the town is just the start. What happens next is a mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/500a2ac6fe34972b4714eb33376ed0b1.poster.avif?t=1758639690\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/500a2ac6fe34972b4714eb33376ed0b1.webm?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137450/extras/500a2ac6fe34972b4714eb33376ed0b1.mp4?t=1758639690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEVELOPMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The project wouldn't be possible without DaveFace's Psx Shader and Horror Engine plug-in for Unreal Engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOCIAL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For development updates, you can follow along on YouTube, Twitter &amp; TikTok.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MUSIC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All music is created by FIFTYFIFTH, Leiwaan,  Delancey Throne &amp; Thomas Hansen.</p>",
